wn the problems. `` There are problems with any new weapon and you do n't find out about some of the problems until you field the system,'' said company spokesman <PERSON> Rob </PERSON> <PERSON> Mack </PERSON>. `` We have heard both good and bad, but we have hear a lot of good.''
